<div class="patternContent"><div class="foswikiTopic"> <h1 id="A_2._System_configuration"> <A name="Section_2."></A>2.  System configuration </h1>
<span id="TableOfContents"></span>
<div class="foswikiToc" id="foswikiTOC"> <ul>
